cs.LG, cs.SI, cs.SY, cs.AI, cs.DS 

The paper discusses the application of machine learning to networks, specifically through network embeddings. This topic falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and could also be classified under social and information networks (cs.SI) and systems and control (cs.SY) due to the focus on network analysis. Additionally, the paper proposes a new algorithm for learning network embeddings, which falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and data structures and algorithms (cs.DS).
